ividuals%20now!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThank%20you!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20all%20those%20readers%20who%20wrote%20in%20to%20wish%20The%20%3Cem%3EWire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20Happy%20New%20Year%2C%20thank%20you.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20wishing%20you%20a%202024%20full%20of%20possibilities%20and%20promise%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20and%20fro%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Thapar%20responded%20to%20a%20letter%20carried%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbackstory-searching-for-the-words-of-2023-amidst-the-rubble-of-gaza%5C%22%3EBackstory%3A%C2%A0Searching%20for%20the%20Words%20of%202023%20Amidst%20the%20Rubble%20of%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Wrong%20Call%E2%80%99%20(%20December%2031)%3A%20%E2%80%98Dear%20Ms.%20Jayaram%2C%20My%20only%20reply%20to%20you%20is%20the%20following%3A%20As%20Jesus%20said%2C%20let%20those%20without%20fault%20be%20the%20first%20to%20cast%20stones.%20I%20am%20not%20faultless.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20possible%20you%20are.%C2%A0Secondly%2C%20if%20journalists%20can%20legitimately%20and%20rightly%20interview%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20all%20that%20he%20has%20said%20and%20done%20and%20is%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%93%20then%20journalists%20can%20interview%20Suhel%20Seth%20with%20as%20much%20right%20and%20credibility.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMr%20Jayaram%20responded%20to%20Mr%20Thapar%3A%20%E2%80%98Dear%20Mr%20Thapar%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CDear%20Ms.%20Jayaram%E2%80%9D%3F%20Albeit%20an%20activist%20of%20sorts%20and%20a%20clicktivist%20backing%20LGBTQIA%2B%20causes%2C%20I%20self-identify%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Che%E2%80%9D%2C%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20mind.%20I%20was%20merely%20drawing%20attention%20to%20NWMI%E2%80%99s%20tweets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Having%20started%20your%20para%201%2C%20with%20Jesus%E2%80%99s%20wisdom%2C%20why%20then%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20possible%20you%20are.%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98That%20said%2C%20I%20remain%20a%20huge%20admirer%20of%20your%20absolutely%20brilliant%20work%20regarding%20the%20horrendous%20tragedy%20befalling%20Palestine%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20your%20work%20in%20support%20of%20secularism%20and%20democracy%20in%20our%20now%20benighted%20land%2C%20and%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20often%20been%20sharing%20on%20FB%3B%20X%3B%20and%20on%20email.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERe-frame%20that%2C%20please!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReader%20N.%20Venkatesh%20takes%20issue%20with%20a%20certain%20framing%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%98In%20the%20Backstory%20of%20December%2031%2C%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbackstory-searching-for-the-words-of-2023-amidst-the-rubble-of-gaza%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESince%C2%A0October%207%2C%20when%C2%A0Hamas%C2%A0invaded%20Israel%20and%20killed%201%2C200%20of%20its%20citizens.%20..%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20You%20should%20be%20aware%20that%20this%20view%20is%20not%C2%A0tenable%20and%20much%20of%20that%20framing%20is%20simply%20incorrect.%20In%20short%3A%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20killed%20the%20most%20on%20that%C2%A0day%20and%20the%20list%20included%20695%20Israeli%20civilians.%C2%A0There%20is%20a%20clutch%C2%A0of%20raw%20material%20and%20analyses%20to%20endorse%20this%20in%20order%20to%20help%20you%20make%20up%20your%20mind.%C2%A0Your%20sentence%20is%20not%20just%20misframed%2C%20it%20does%20injustice%20to%20the%20reality.%20There%20are%20literally%20hundreds%20of%20UN%20resolutions%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FUnited_Nations_General_Assembly_Resolution_3379%5C%22%3E1973%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20against%20Zionism.%20It%20invalidated%20Israel-as-a-state%20and%20instead%20recognised%C2%A0the%20right%20of%20return%20of%20Palestinians.%20So%20a%20better%20phrasing%2C%20avoiding%20standard%20mainstream%20framing%20orthodoxies%2C%20would%20go%20like%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20finally%20began%20the%20liberation%20campaign%20of%20Palestine%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98I%20would%20have%20loved%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dissident%20outlet%20%E2%80%93%20to%20do%20better.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20response%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%98Thank%20you%20for%20your%20mail%2C%20N.%20Venkatesh%2C%20but%20I%20beg%20to%20differ%20with%20you.%20The%20liberation%20campaign%20for%20Palestine%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20decades%2C%20well%20before%20the%20emergence%20of%20Hamas.%20Armed%20resistance%20has%20been%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20past%20by%20different%20groups%2C%20including%20Fatah%2C%20the%20Popular%20Front%20for%20the%20Liberation%20of%20Palestine%20and%20the%20Popular%20Democratic%20Front%20for%20the%20Liberation%20of%20Palestine.%20Indeed%2C%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20October%207%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20attack%20could%20be%20considered%20a%20strategic%20setback%2C%20since%20it%20provided%20Israel%20with%20an%20excuse%20to%20conduct%20its%20present%20genocidal%20campaign%20against%20Palestinians.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%2C%20of%20course%2C%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20can%20in%20any%20way%20be%20justified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98As%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdissident%20outlet%E2%80%9D%2C%20perhaps%20it%20would%20be%20more%20appropriate%20to%20consider%20it%20as%20a%20staunchly%20independent%20yet%20responsible%20news%20portal.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnd%20note%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20ever-alert%20Churimuri%20recently%20drew%20our%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20biggest%20donor%20to%20electoral%20trusts%20