%20the%20brains%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20the%20star%20is%20and%20who%20the%20supporting%20cast%20in%20this%20glitzy%20celebration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20leaving%20alone%20the%20Almighty%20from%20this%20blasphemous%20false%20equivalence%2C%20we%20know%20who%20the%20chosen%20one%20is%20in%20our%20benighted%20country%20because%20we%20have%20his%20word%20for%20it.%20In%20a%20special%20audio%20message%20released%20on%20January%2012%2C%20announcing%20a%20special%20ritual%20ahead%20of%20the%20grand%20event%20%E2%80%93%20a%2011-day%20%E2%80%98anushsthan%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20a%20government%20that%20is%20still%20officially%20secular%2C%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20state%20that%20%E2%80%9CGod%20(no%20less)%20has%20chosen%20me%20to%20represent%20the%20people%20of%20India%20during%20pran%20pratishta%E2%80%9D.%20Shortly%20thereafter%20came%20the%20endorsement%20from%20modern%20India%E2%80%99s%20Iron%20man-turned-yes-man%20who%20issued%20a%20public%20statement%20that%20Modi%20had%20been%20chosen%20by%20Lord%20Ram%20to%20preside%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20no%20mistake%3B%20we%20are%20beholding%20an%20extraordinary%20human%20phenomenon%20who%20has%20upended%20all%20the%20conventional%20norms%20of%20leadership.%20Self-awareness%2C%20humility%2C%20and%20respectfulness%20as%20personal%20traits%2C%20the%20assumption%20that%20the%20PM%20is%20only%20first%20among%20equals%2C%20collective%20decision-making%2C%20team%20spirit%2C%20and%20empowering%20delegation%20are%20attributes%20of%20leadership%20that%20Modi%20has%20contemptuously%20discarded.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20the%20entire%20polity%20%E2%80%93%20humans%20and%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20has%20slavishly%20revolved%20around%20this%20superman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20playing%20out%20before%20the%20country%20is%20an%20extreme%20form%20of%20deification.%20His%20devotees%20see%20him%20variously%20as%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20as%20an%20avatar%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20as%20the%2011th%20avatar%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu.%20J.P.%20Nadda%20%E2%80%93%20sycophant%20supreme%20%E2%80%93%20went%20over%20the%20top%2C%20describing%20his%20master%20as%20the%20king%20of%20Gods.%20Going%20beyond%20mere%20verbalism%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20Modi%20temple%20in%20the%20Rajkot%20district%20of%20Gujarat%20and%2C%20if%20media%20reports%20are%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20another%20one%20on%20the%20anvil%20in%20Meerut%20embellished%20with%20a%20100-foot%20statue%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-579092%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20might%20of%20government%20has%20been%20mobilised%20to%20project%20one%20man%20and%20his%20achievements%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantees%2C%20not%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20apocryphal.%20Even%20criminal%20failures%20like%20the%20botched%20pandemic%20response%20are%20transformed%20through%20a%20bizarre%20alchemic%20process%20into%20unmitigated%20triumphs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20shocker%20is%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Feconomists-say-niti-aayog-claims-on-poverty-reduction-distort-the-truth%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520multidimensional%2520measure%2520looks%2520at%2Cescaping%2520poverty%2520during%2520this%2520period.%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20claims%20a%20precipitate%20reduction%20in%20poverty%20levels.%20Through%20statistical%20sleight%20of%20hand%2C%20brilliantly%20described%20by%20one%20commentator%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmagical%20realism%E2%80%9D%2C%20multidimensional%20poverty%20is%20shown%20to%20have%20declined%20from%2029.1%25%20in%202013-14%20to%2011.28%25%20in%202022-23%2C%20thereby%20lifting%20about%2024.82%20crore%20people%20out%20of%20poverty.%20(What%20then%20does%20one%20make%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20of%20providing%20foodgrains%20to%20more%20than%2080%20crore%20people%20free%20of%20cost%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%20%E2%80%93%20a%20case%20of%20carrying%20coal%20to%20Newcastle%3F)%20With%20the%20truth%20undermined%20and%20the%20distinction%20between%20fact%20and%20fantasy%20blurred%2C%20our%20Supreme%20Leader%20parades%20one%20falsehood%20after%20another%20with%20a%20disarming%20straight%20face!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20unabated%2C%20all-out%20government%20propaganda%20promoting%20our%20tinsel%20god%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20more%20in-your-face%20in%20its%20unblushing%20projection%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20than%20the%20legislated%20diktat%20%E2%80%93%20flagrantly%20intended%20to%20stimulate%20cult%20worship%20%E2%80%93%20directing%20universities%20and%20Indian%20Railways%20to%20set%20up%20selfie%20points%20at%20select%20locations%20and%20stations%20with%20pictures%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20presumably%20to%20enable%20us%20to%20bask%20in%20reflected%20glory.%20There%20are%20official%20instructions%20to%20army%20men%20proceeding%20on%20leave%2C%20and%20sundry%20government%20officials%2C%20to%20tom-tom%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Modi%20sarkar.%20So%20universal%20is%20the%20plague%20that%20even%20our%20Covid%20vaccination%20certificates%20and%20the%205%20kg%20rice%20bags%20given%20as%20dole%20have%20our%20Supreme%20Leader%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20picture%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20the%20government%20but%20the%20BJP%20too%20has%20capitulated%20to%20the%20cult%20worship.%20Everybody%20else%20has%20been%20smudged%20out%2C%20including%20redoubtable%20stalwarts%20like%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi.%20Possible%20competitors%20of%20his%20alter%20ego%20such%20as%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Shivraj%20Chauhan%2C%20and%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20insignificance.%20By%20picking%20nonentities%20as%20chief%20ministers%20in%20the%20three%20States%20where%20the%20BJP%20recently%20won%20big%2C%20the%20clear%20message%20conveyed%20was%20that%20it%20is%20one%20man%20alone%20who%20wins%20elections%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Everyone%20else%20is%20dispensible!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20are%20witnessing%20today%20is%20no%20ordinary%20case%20of%20a%20leader%20in%20an%20exalted%20state%20of%20self-love%20or%20self-absorption%3B%20one%20suspects%20a%20deeper%20pathology%20that%20psychoanalysts%20have%20identified%20as%20narcissism.%20Equally%20unhinged%20is%20the%20ignoble%20servitude%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20devotees%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20come%20under%20the%20spell%20of%20this%20consummate%20artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErich%20Fromm%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20psychoanalysts%20and%20social%20philosophers%2C%20who%20has%20delved%20deep%20into%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20narcissist%20and%20his%20symbiotic%20connection%20with%20his%20submissive%20%E2%80%9Cmasochistic%E2%80%9D%20devotee%2C%20helps%20us%20understand%20the%20bizarre%20idol%20worship%20in%20our%20country%20today.%20According%20to%20Fromm%2C%20man%E2%80%99s%20sanity%20depends%20on%20his%20relatedness%20and%20communion%20with%20other%20human%20beings.%20This%20transcending%20of%20lonely%20individual%20existence%20and%20unifying%20with%20the%20other%20humans%20is%20achieved%20by%20the%20narcissist%20through%20domination%20and%20by%20the%20bhakt%20through%20submission%20but%20in%20the%20process%20of%20feeding%20on%20each%20other%2C%20they%20both%20lose%20their%20integrity%20and%20freedom.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20lose%20the%20capacity%20for%20the%20one%20passion%20that%20inspires%20solidarity%20with%20our%20fellow%20creatures%20which%20is%20love%20and%20empathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20very%20abstruse%3F%20Put%20simply%2C%20the%20narcissist%20fails%20to%20develop%20the%20capacity%20for%20love%20because%20for%20him%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20only%20one%20reality%2C%20that%20of%20his%20own%20thought%20processes%2C%20feelings%20and%20needs%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Emotionally%20crippled%2C%20the%20narcissist%20sees%20the%20phenomena%20in%20the%20outside%20world%20only%20from%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20them%20being%20useful%20or%20dangerous%20to%20him.%20Fromm%20believes%20that%20in%20its%20most%20extreme%20form%2C%20narcissism%20can%20lead%20to%20insanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20submissive%20masochists%2C%20what%20is%20particularly%20disconcerting%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20overwhelming%20millions%20among%20us%20have%20enthusiastically%20bought%20into%20his%20overweening%20narcissism%20and%20sophistry.%20Which%20brings%20to%20mind%20Shakespeare%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20diagnosis%20of%20why%20the%20egomaniacal%20Julius%20Caesar%20held%20sway%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%20doth%20bestride%20the%20narrow%20world%20like%20a%20Colossus%2C%20and%20we%20petty%20men%20walk%20under%20his%20huge%20legs%2C%20and%20peep%20about%20to%20find%20ourselves%20dishonourable%20graves%E2%80%A6.The%20fault%20dear%20Brutus%20is%20not%20in%20our%20stars%2C%20but%20in%20ourselves%2C%20that%20we%20are%20underlings%E2%80%A6.upon%20what%20meat%20(or%20dhokla)%20doth%20this%20our%20Caesar%20feed%20that%20he%20is%20grown%20so%20great%3F%E2%80%9D%20Shame%20on%20us!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705756813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fof-narcissism-and-submissive-masochism%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20we%20are%20witnessing%20today%20is%20no%20ordinary%20case%20of%20a%20leader%20in%20an%20exalted%20state%20of%20self-love%20or%20self-absorption.%20Equally%20unhinged%20is%20the%20ignoble%20servitude%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20devotees%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20come%20under%20the%20spell%20of%20this%20consummate%20artist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fof-narcissism-and-submissive-masochism%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mortgage%20rates%20will%20dip%20below%206%25%20this%20year%20amid%20a%20stronger%20housing-market%20rebound%2C%20Fannie%20Mae%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20housing%20market%20is%20starting%20to%20unfreeze.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a955efdcdb354a98589c5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20housing%20market%20is%20starting%20to%20unfreeze.%3Cp%3EC.J.%20Burton%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFannie%20Mae%20now%20sees%20mortgage%20rates%20dipping%20below%206%25%20in%202024%2C%20anticipating%20a%20stronger%20housing%20market%20rebound.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2030-year%20fixed%20rate%20is%20expected%20to%20hit%205.8%25%20by%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20down%20from%20a%20previous%20estimate%20of%206.5%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outlook%20for%20both%20short%20term%20rates%20and%20mortgage%20rates%20is%20now%20decidedly%20lower%20than%20what%20we%20had%20previously%20forecast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20market%20will%20thaw%20faster%20than%20expected%20with%20mortgages%20dipping%20below%206%25%20later%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Fannie%20Mae%2C%20which%20sharply%20revised%20its%20forecasts%20from%20just%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20as%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20has%20signaled%20a%20pivot%20away%20from%20tight%20monetary%20policy%2C%20sending%20bond%20yields%20lower%2C%20along%20with%20other%20borrowing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20anticipate%20that%20after%20the%20past%20several%20years%20of%20extreme%20volatility%20in%20interest%20rates%2C%20the%2030-year%20fixed%20rate%20mortgage%20rate%20will%20continue%20to%20moderate%20over%20the%20course%20of%202024%2C%20moving%20toward%20a%20rate%20below%206%25%20by%20year%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Fannie%20Mae's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanniemae.com%2Fmedia%2F50186%2Fdisplay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20market%20outlook%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hitting%208%25%20in%20October%2C%20the%20average%2030-year%20fixed%20rate%20has%20already%20fallen%20to%206.60%25%20as%20of%20Thursday%20from%206.66%25%20in%20the%20week%20prior%2C%20sister%20mortgage%20giant%20Freddie%20Mac%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Fannie%20Mae%20sees%20a%20steeper%20decline%20from%20there%2C%20predicting%20a%20rate%20of%205.8%25%20by%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%20and%205.5%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20That's%20down%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanniemae.com%2Fmedia%2F49866%2Fdisplay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDecember%20forecast%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%206.5%25%20for%20late%2