crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeeks%20later%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20the%20land%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20for%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20price%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%203.57%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20City%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Time%20City%20group%20founded%20by%20Chandra%20Prakash%20Shukla%2C%20a%20former%20chartered%20accountant%20with%20the%20Sahara%20group%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20was%20an%20MLA%20from%20Kaptanganj%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20The%20group%20is%20run%20by%20Shukla%E2%80%99s%20former%20business%20associate%2C%20Pankaj%20Pathak%20%E2%80%93%20a%20BJP%20member%2C%20who%20the%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20says%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20friends%20in%20the%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP%20party%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20deal%2C%20it%20was%20the%20farmers%20who%20sold%20the%20land%20for%20a%20cheap%20throwaway%20price.%20The%20land%20deal%20also%20raises%20many%20ecological%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20Time%20City%20bought%20a%20hectare%20of%20land%20in%20Majha%20Jamthara.%20That%20land%20belonged%20to%20the%20families%20of%20Ghanseera%20Yadav%20and%20Kabootra%20Devi%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20in%20Majha%20Jamthara%20that%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20is%20part%20of%20the%20environmentally%20sensitive%20wetland%20near%20Saryu%2C%20a%20habitat%20of%20the%20Sarus%20crane%2C%20grey%20heron%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20fox.%20Since%20December%202022%2C%20the%20government%20has%20prohibited%20any%20new%20construction%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajha%20Jamthara%20is%20a%20vast%2C%20unpopulated%20region%20between%20Faizabad%2C%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Saryu%20river%20%E2%80%93%20about%205%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20Ram%20temple%20being%20built%20on%20the%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EScroll%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20questions%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Adani%20group%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20transaction%20carried%20out%20by%20%5Bone%20of%20its%20subsidiaries%5D%20is%20completely%20legal%20and%20has%20been%20conducted%20in%20accordance%20with%20all%20laws%20and%20regulations.%20The%20company%20acquired%20land%20at%20the%20prevailing%20circle%20rates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScroll%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20investigation%20has%20further%20found%20that%20in%20February%202021%2C%20the%20Yadavs%20sold%200.56%20hectares%20of%20the%20land%20they%20had%20inherited%20to%20Sudha%20Dixit%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kanpur%2C%20for%20Rs%2033.53%20lakh%20over%20two%20transactions.%20This%20amount%20is%20significantly%20below%20the%20land%E2%80%99s%20circle%20rate%20(minimum)%20price%2C%20which%20the%20report%20claims%20then%20stood%20at%20Rs%2077.46%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20witness%20in%20both%20these%20transactions%20was%20Suryabhan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20legal%20advisor%20to%20Time%20City%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20expose%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20Dixit%20sold%20this%20property%20to%20Time%20City%20for%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20over%20two%20sale%20deeds%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20two%20separate%20transactions.%20The%20witnesses%20in%20both%20the%20sale%20deeds%20were%20Jaibhan%20Singh%20and%20Avinash%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Yadavs%20sold%20another%20land%20parcel%20of%200.44%20hectare%20directly%20Time%20City%20for%20Rs%2033%20lakh.%20This%20time%20too%20the%20deal%20was%20much%20below%20the%20circle%20price%20and%C2%A0%C2%A0the%20witnesses%20in%20the%20deal%20were%20Avinash%20Singh%20and%20Sitaram%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20witnesses%20in%20these%20three%20transactions%20are%20linked%20to%20local%20BJP%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryabhan%20and%20Jaibhan%20are%20brothers%20of%20Chandrabhan%20Singh%2C%20a%20BJP%20worker%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20zila%20pancha