l%20LeBaron.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELeBaron%20ordered%20his%20followers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20his%20wives%20and%20children%20%E2%80%94%20to%20commit%20dozens%20of%20murders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20LeBaron%20saga%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20ABC%20docuseries%C2%A0%26quot%3BDaughters%20of%20the%20Cult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20look%20at%20them%2C%20you%20would%20never%20know%20that%20Celia%20and%20Anna%20LeBaron%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20violent%20cult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20LeBaron%20sisters%20are%20in%20their%2050s%2C%20energetic%20with%20kind%20eyes%20%E2%80%94%20the%20type%20of%20women%20to%20run%20a%20PTA%20meeting%20or%20throw%20a%20block%20party.%20Yet%20both%20survived%20brainwashing%2C%20biblical%20indoctrination%2C%20and%20neglect%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20cold%20night%20in%20January%2C%20Celia%20and%20Anna%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20from%20their%20respective%20homes%20in%20Dallas%20about%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20the%20polygamist%20Church%20of%20the%20Lamb%20of%20God%2C%20a%20radical%20offshoot%20of%20Mormonism%20where%20their%20father%2C%20Ervil%20LeBaron%2C%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20one%20true%20prophet%20of%20God.%20Ervil's%20belief%20in%20his%20own%20divine%20power%20led%20him%20to%20murder%20anyone%20who%20disagreed%2C%20including%20some%20of%20his%20own%20brothers%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20crimes%20and%20the%20cult%20are%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20new%20ABC%20News%20documentary%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D62a89e5fd13520eaa5a367acf4966293f2c157f5b052f2e6a66a7faba54ea011%26postID%3D65a82e8ed137673d8ca09808%26postSlug%3Ddaughters-of-the-cult-anna-and-celia-lebaron-speak-2024-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hulu.com%252Fseries%252Fecb95c0a-c542-4716-8320-24e0a67e133b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDaughters%20of%20the%20Cult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelia%20and%20Anna%20say%20they%20barely%20knew%20their%20father%20%E2%80%94%20Anna%20only%20recalls%20meeting%20him%20twice.%20They%20were%20just%20two%20of%20more%20than%2050%20children%20Ervil%20fathered%20with%20his%2013%20wives.%20But%20his%20presence%20and%20his%20crimes%20loomed%20large%20over%20their%20lives.%20The%20family%20constantly%20moved%20around%20to%20protect%20Ervil%2C%20traveling%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Mexico.%20As%20children%2C%20Anna%20and%20Celia%20could%20spend%20months%20away%20from%20their%20mother%2C%20living%20instead%20with%20a%20far-flung%20half-sister%20or%20member%20of%20the%20church%20in%20sub-poverty%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinding%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20took%20me%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Anna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20faked%20it%20till%20I%20made%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Celia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20yearslong%20killing%20spree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20photo%20of%20Ervil%20LeBaron%20pinned%20to%20a%20police%20pegboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaf1a6dcdb354a9859598d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnna%20and%20Celia's%20father%20Ervil%20LeBaron.%3Cp%3EABC%20News%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EErvil%20LeBaron%20was%20one%20of%20four%20sons%20of%20Alma%20Dayer%20LeBaron%2C%20Sr.%2C%20a%20polygamist%20Mormon%20who%20established%20a%20community%20in%20Mexico%20%E2%80%94%20Colonia%20LeBaron%20%E2%80%94%20after%20the%20church%20formally%20rejected%20the%20practice%20of%20polygamy.%20When%20Alma%20died%20in%201951%2C%20leadership%20of%20the%20church%20was%20passed%20on%20to%20Ervil's%20brother%20Joel.%20Joel%20established%20the%20Church%20of%20the%20Firstborn%20of%20the%20Fulness%20of%20Times%20and%20ran%20it%20for%20around%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20early%20'70s%2C%20Ervil%20had%20broken%20off%20from%20Joel%20to%20form%20the%20Church%20of%20the%20First%20Born%20Lamb%20of%20God.%20Ervil%20and%20his%20followers%20believed%20in%20blood%20atonement%2C%20a%20long-abandoned%20practice%20in%20which%20the%20blood%20of%20sinners%20needed%20to%20be%20shed%20in%20order%20for%20them%20to%20ascend%20to%20heaven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20the%20justification%20for%20a%20yearslong%20killing%20spree.%20First%2C%20Ervil%20took%20out%20his%20brother%20Joel%2C%20and%20then%20he%20began%20targeting%20leaders%20of%20competing%20religious%20sects%20and%20cult%20members%20he%20believed%20were%20a%20threat%20to%20him.%20In%201981%2C%20after%20several%20years%20of%20living%20on%20the%20run%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1981%2F08%2F17%2Fobituaries%2Fervil-lebaron-utah-polygamist-is-found-dead-in-his-prison-cell.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EErvil%20was%20sentenced%20to%20life%20in%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20being%20found%20guilty%20of%20ordering%20the%20death%20of%20sect%20leader%20Rulon%20Allred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErvil%20died%20in%20prison%20in%201981%20but%20continued%20to%20lead%20his%20followers%20from%20beyond%20the%20grave%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Book%20of%20the%20New%20Covenants%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20rambling%20400-page%20text%20he'd%20written%20while%20behind%20bars.%20Hidden%20within%20it%20was%20a%20list%20of%2050%20people%20Ervil%20demanded%20his%20followers%20blood%20atone.%20His%20sons%20Heber%20and%20Aaron%20took%20charge%20and%20began%20ruthlessly%20working%20their%20way%20through%20the%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20two%20sepia%20toned%20photos%20of%20two%20young%20men%20on%20a%20pegboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaf1e66979d73718251089%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeber%20LeBaron%20(left)%20and%20Aaron%20LeBaron%20carried%20out%20several%20murders%20in%20their%20father's%20name.%20%3Cp%3EABC%20News%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20murder%20spree%20culminated%20in%20what%20became%20known%20as%20the%20Four%20O'clock%20Murders%2C%20in%20which%20three%20men%20and%20a%20child%20were%20killed%20at%20the%20same%20time%20on%20June%2027%2C%201988%2C%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Joseph%20Smith.%20Heber%20and%20Aaron%2C%20their%20sister%20Patricia%2C%20and%20another%20man%20were%20found%20guilty%20of%20the%20murders.%20They%20each%20received%20sentences%20ranging%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deseret.com%2F1997%2F6%2F13%2F19317679%2Flebaron-gets-45-year-sentence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E45%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20life.%20Their%20brother%20Richard%20was%20a%20cooperating%20witness%20and%20received%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deseret.com%2F1993%2F11%2F27%2F19078632%2Fex-member-of-cult-gets-5-years-for-slaying-man-and-daughter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive-year%20sentence.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20point%2C%20both%20Celia%20and%20Anna%20were%20out%20of%20the%20church.%20While%20Anna%20had%20run%20away%20from%20home%20in%201980%20when%20she%20was%2013%2C%20it%20took%20Celia%20several%20more%20years%20to%20leave%20%E2%80%94%20her%20breaking%20point%20was%20being%20told%20she%20couldn't%20complete%20her%20senior%20year%20of%20high%20school.%20Neither%20of%20them%20had%20any%20idea%20that%20their%20father%20and%20his%20followers%20had%20waged%20such%20a%20violent%20campaign%20of%20terror%20until%20their%20brothers'%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20chaotic%20childhood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22four%20people%20hugging%20outdoors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaf38adcdb354a98595bf0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnna%20and%20Celia%20meet%20up%20with%20two%20of%20their%20siblings.%20%3Cp%3EABC%20News%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20children%2C%20the%20sisters%20say%20they%20often%20went%20without%20food.%20They%20lived%20an%20itinerant%20life%2C%20often%20moving%20between%20run-down%20shacks%20without%20running%20water%20or%20electricity.%20Ervil%20saw%20the%20children%20as%20an%20inexpensive%20labor%20force%2C%20and%20put%20them%20to%20work%20for%20the%20family's%20appliance%20repair%20store.%20At%20age%209%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodhousekeeping.com%2Flife%2Fa43068%2Fpolygamists-daughter-excerpt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnna%20was%20sent%20to%20Mexico%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20she%20could%20be%20appraised%20by%20the%20man%20her%20father%20had%20promised%20her%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChurch%20doctrine%20said%20that%20children%20who%20misbehaved%20could%20be%20stoned%20to%20death%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Ten%20Commandments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20in%20the%20Old%20Testament.%20That's%20the%20commandment%3A%20honor%20thy%20father%20and%20thy%20mother%2C%26quot%3B%20Celia%20said.%20%26quot%3BMeaning%20if%20you%20don't%20obey%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20rebellious%20child%2C%20get%20stoned%20to%20death.%20We%20were%20raised%20on%20that%20all%20our%20lives.%20You%20knew%20that%20growing%20up%2C%20you%20were%20aware%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20mother%2C%20Anna-Mae%20LeBaron%2C%20blindly%20followed%20Ervil's%20doctrine%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20it%20meant%20abandoning%20her%20children%20for%20long%20stretches%20of%20time%20to%20travel%20with%20Ervil%20as%20his%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20raised%20with%20a%20mother%20who%20frequently%20disappeared%20for%20long%20stretches%20profoundly%20impacted%20how%20Celia%20and%20Anna%20parented%20their%20own%20children.%20Celia%20said%20she%20raised%20her%20three%20now-adult%20kids%20with%20attachment-style%20parenting.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20my%20babies%20were%20never%20without%20me%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20wanted%20them%20to%20ever%20feel%20insecure%20about%20where%20I%20was.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20admits%20that%20she%20parented%20her%20five%20kids%20from%20a%20place%20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20my%20faith%20in%20the%20world%20and%20faith%20in%20the%20goodness%20of%20others%2C%20I%20parented%20from%20fear%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20impacted%20them%20to%20some%20degree%20because%20I%20didn't%20really%20trust%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20even%20though%20we%20were%20part%20of%20it%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Anna%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20stability%20she%20was%20able%20to%20give%20her%20children.%20They%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20house%20for%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20five%20of%20my%20kids%20graduated%20from%20the%20same%20school.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20create%20that%20safety%20and%20stability%20for%20my%20children%20that%20my%20parents%20weren't%20able%20to%20do%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20possible%20to%20create%20a%20different%20life%20than%20the%20one%20you%20were%20born%20or%20raised%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20for%20answers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20white%20woman%20with%20bangs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaf300dcdb354a98595b4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelia%20LeBaron%20says%20her%20mother%20eventually%20apologized%20to%20her%20and%20admitted%20that%20her%20father%20Ervil%20was%20not%20a%20prophet.%20%3Cp%3EABC%20News%20Studio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20mother's%20death%20in%202019%2C%20Celia%20and%20Anna%20each%20confronted%20her%20about%20their%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20we%20were%20quite%20often%20neglected%2C%20even%20as%20little%20children.%20I%20remember%20asking%20my%20mom%2C%20'How%20could%20you%20do%20that%3F%20How%20could%20you%20just%20let%20us%20run%20around%20and%20not%20have%20supervision%20and%20not%20be%20watching%20us%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20us%3F'%26quot%3B%20Celia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Btrusted%20God%26quot%3B%20to%20care%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20weak-minded%20and%20brainwashed%20and%20allowed%20her%20children%20to%20suffer%2C%20effectively%20sacrificing%20us%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20her%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Anna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20we%20were%20just%20Isaac%20right%20there%20on%20her%20altar%2C%26quot%3B%20Celia%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Celia%20said%2C%20her%20mother%20%26quot%3Bapologized%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20yes%2C%20Ervil%20was%20not%20a%20prophet%2C%20and%20what%20you%20went%20through%20was%20not%20your%20fault.%20Abuses%20that%20were%20put%20upon%20your%20head%20were%20not%20fair%20or%20right.%20Her%20saying%20that%20to%20me%2C%20that%20it%20was%20wrong%20and%20you%20didn't%20deserve%20that%2C%20was%20quite%20healing%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Anna%2C%20the%20moment%20came%20as%20she%20was%20working%20on%20her%202017%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Polygamist's%20Daughter%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20she%20went%20public%20about%20her%20traumatic%20childhood%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20didn't%20want%20her%20to%20sit%20and%20read%20that%20book%20by%20herself.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20going%20to%20break%20her%20heart%20to%20read%20those%20things.%20So%20I%20showed%20up%20with%20the%20book%20and%20we%20sat%20and%20read%20the%20whole%20manuscript.%20I%20read%20the%20whole%20thing%20to%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Anna%20said.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20of%20us%20cried%20and%20cried%20and%20cried.%20it%20was%20healing%20for%20me%20to%20see%20her%20grief%20over%20my%20suffering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Celia%20and%20Anna%20LeBaron%20attempted%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20their%20relatives%20in%20prison.%20Anna%20has%20periodically%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Aaron%20and%20Heber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20open%20to%20all%20of%20that%20because%20what%20I%20do%20know%20about%20all%20of%20them%20is%20there's%20not%20one%20single%20one%20of%20them%2C%20even%20the%20ones%20serving%20time%20in%20prison%2C%20who%20believe%20in%20Ervil%20LeBaron's%20teachings%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelia%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20Heber%20at%20one%20point%20but%20said%20receiving%20his%20letters%20put%20her%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20emotional%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20he%20said%20in%20one%20of%20his%20letters%20was%20'you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20afraid%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Celia%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20responded%20back%2C%20I%20said%2C%20'I'm%20not%20afraid%20of%20you.%20I'm%20afraid%20of%20your%20religion.'%20Because%20I%20knew%20my%20brother%20was%20a%20gentle%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20no%20longer%20speaks%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelia%20recognizes%20that%20it%20could%20have%20just%20as%20likely%20been%20her%20that%20committed%20crimes%20for%20Ervil%2C%20recalling%20how%20blood%20atonement%20was%20taught%20to%20her%20and%20the%20other%20children%20from%20a%20young%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20fully%20indoctrinated%2C%20had%20my%20brain%20twisted%20about%20how%20taking%20someone's%20life%20helps%20them%20get%20to%20heaven%20because%20they%20get%20to%20atone%20for%20their%20sin%20and%20not%20have%20to%20spend%20their%20life%20in%20outer%20darkness%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20something%20we%20were%20taught%20%E2%80%94%20that%20you're%20actually%20helping%20these%20people%20by%20taking%20their%20lives.%20That's%20really%20such%20a%20warped%20way%20of%20believing%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20were%20taught.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Anna%20believes%20that%20her%20relatives%20%E2%80%94%20even%20those%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20crimes%20%E2%80%94%20deserve%20fresh%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20the%20brainwashing%2C%20none%20of%20them%20were%20dangerous.%20They%20were%20good%2C%20good%20people%2C%20and%20their%20brains%20were%20just%20twisted%20with%20this%20horrible%2C%20sickening%20doctrine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20once%20they%20were%20able%20to%20think%20for%20themselves%20and%20get%20out%20of%20the%20cult%2C%20they%20became%20the%20good%20people%20that%20they%20always%20had%20been.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaughters-of-the-cult-anna-and-celia-lebaron-speak-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705753141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaef7743bb77284b9edfe2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaughters-of-the-cult-anna-and-celia-lebaron-speak-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anna%20and%20Celia%20LeBaron%20survived%20their%20father%20Ervil's%20deadly%20cult.%20They%20spoke%20with%20BI%20about%20their%20new%20docuseries%2C%20%26quot%3BDaughters%20of%20the%20Cult.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jgerstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Julie%20Gerstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaughters-of-the-cult-anna-and-celia-lebaron-speak-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sundance%20Winner%20Sofia%20Alaoui%20to%20Tackle%20Eco-Anxieties%20in%20Apocalyptic%20Thriller%20%E2%80%98Tarfaya%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98This%20World%20Is%20Full%20of%20Poetry%20and%20Melancholy%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705753062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSofia-Alaoui.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%2