0platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfakes%20are%20a%20form%20of%20synthetic%20media%20crafted%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20employing%20sophisticated%20algorithms%20to%20manipulate%20both%20visual%20and%20audio%20elements.%20The%20term%20gained%20prominence%20in%202017%20when%20a%20Reddit%20user%20introduced%20a%20platform%20for%20sharing%20manipulated%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20deepfake%20technology%20has%20evolved%2C%20becoming%20a%20potential%20weapon%20for%20cybercriminals%20to%20disrupt%20and%20damage%20the%20reputation%20of%20individuals%2C%20companies%2C%20or%20even%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20IT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20recently%20that%20notices%20were%20sent%20to%20all%20social%20media%20companies%20directing%20them%20to%20take%20necessary%20steps%20to%20identify%20and%20remove%20disinformation%20from%20their%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepfake%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20We%20recently%20issued%20notices%20to%20all%20the%20big%20social%20media%20forms%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20identify%20deepfakes%2C%20for%20removing%20those%20content.%20The%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20responded.%20They%20are%20taking%20action.%20We%20have%20told%20them%20to%20be%20more%20aggressive%20in%20this%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20we%20must%20notice%20that%20the%20'Safe%20Harbour'%20Clause%20that%20most%20of%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20been%20enjoying%2C%20doesn't%20apply%20if%20the%20platforms%20do%20not%20take%20adequate%20steps%20to%20remove%20the%20deepfakes%20from%20their%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Ms%20Mandanna%2C%20deepfake%20videos%20of%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20and%20even%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705752000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2