%3A%22Rs%2010%2C000%20Crore%20Every%2015%20Years%20-%20Cost%20Of%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20would%20require%20an%20estimated%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20every%2015%20years%20to%20procure%20new%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20if%20simultaneous%20polls%20are%20held%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20according%20to%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20communication%20sent%20to%20the%20government%2C%20the%20Commission%20noted%20that%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20EVMs%20was%2015%20years%20and%20one%20set%20of%20machines%20could%20be%20used%20to%20conduct%20three%20cycles%20of%20elections%20in%20their%20life%20span%20if%20simultaneous%20polls%20were%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20estimates%2C%20a%20total%20of%2011.8%20lakh%20polling%20stations%20would%20be%20required%20to%20be%20set%20up%20across%20India%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20two%20sets%20of%20EVMs%20would%20be%20needed%20per%20polling%20station%20--%20one%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20another%20for%20assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20past%20experiences%2C%20the%20EC%20said%20in%20the%20communication%20sent%20to%20the%20government%2C%20certain%20percentage%20of%20Control%20Units%20(CUs)%2C%20Ballot%20Units%20(BUs)%20and%20Voter-Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20machines%20are%20required%20as%20reserves%20to%20replace%20defective%20units%20at%20different%20stages%2C%20including%20on%20election%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20one%20BU%2C%20one%20CU%20and%20one%20VVPAT%20machine%20make%20up%20for%20one%20EVM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20in%20mind%20various%20aspects%2C%20the%20minimum%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20required%20for%20simultaneous%20polls%20would%20be%3A%2046%2C75%2C100%20BUs%2C%2033%2C63%2C300%20CUs%20and%2036%2C62%2C600%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20Commission%20said%20in%20its%20letter%20to%20the%20Law%20Ministry%20in%20February%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20the%20tentative%20cost%20of%20EVM%20stood%20at%20Rs%207%2C900%20per%20BU%2C%20Rs%209%2C800%20per%20CU%20and%20Rs%2016%2C000%20per%20unit%20of%20VVPAT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20questionnaire%20on%20simultaneous%20polls%20sent%20by%20the%20Law%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20panel%20also%20underlined%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20polling%20and%20security%20personnel%2C%20enhanced%20storage%20facilities%20for%20EVMs%20and%20more%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20said%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20production%20of%20new%20machines%2C%20increasing%20warehousing%20facilities%20and%20other%20logistical%20issues%2C%20the%20first%20simultaneous%20elections%20can%20only%20be%20held%20in%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20observed%20that%20five%20articles%20of%20the%20Constitution%20will%20need%20amendments%20to%20hold%20simultaneous%20polls%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provisions%20which%20would%20need%20amendment%20are%20Article%2083%20which%20related%20to%20the%20duration%20of%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Article%2085%20relating%20to%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20the%20President%2C%20Article%20172%20relating%20to%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20state%20legislatures%2C%20Article%20174%20relating%20to%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20state%20legislatures%2C%20and%20Article%20356%20relating%20to%20the%20imposition%20of%20President's%20Rule%20in%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20Tenth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20relating%20to%20disqualification%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20defection%20will%20also%20require%20necessary%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20panel%2C%20headed%20by%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20to%20examine%20the%20issue%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%20the%20country%20has%20been%20renamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Level%20Committee%20on%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20examining%20and%20making%20recommendation%20for%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20assemblies%2C%20municipalities%20and%20panchayats%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20existing%20framework%20under%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20other%20statutory%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705751520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3c48m3f8_election-generic-evm-generic-istock_625x300_01_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20would%20require%20an%20estimated%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20every%2015%20years%20to%20procure%20new%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20if%20simultaneous%20polls%20are%20held%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20according%20to%20the%20poll%20body.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%3A%20Doctors%20Perform%20C-Sections%20Without%20Anaesthesia%2C%20Newborns%20Desperate%20for%20Aid%20Supplies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%