vernor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20at%20the%20time%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20year%2C%20when%20he%20claimed%20the%20terror%20attack%20was%20a%20result%20of%20%E2%80%9Cincompetence%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Elaparwahi%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20the%20Indian%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatya-pal-malik-full-interview-pulwama-modi%5C%22%3EPulwama%2C%20Modi%2C%20Corruption%3A%20Full%20Explosive%20Transcript%20of%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20Viral%20Interview%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20envoy%20was%20also%20asked%20what%20proof%20exists%20to%20corroborate%20the%20statement%20made%20by%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20of%20the%20time%2C%20which%20Bisaria%20quotes%20in%20his%20book.%20The%20statement%20is%20that%20at%20Balakot%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20very%20large%20number%20of%20JeM%20terrorists%2C%20trainers%2C%20senior%20commanders%2C%20and%20groups%20of%20jihadis%2C%20who%20were%20being%20trained%20for%20fidayeen%20action%2C%20were%20eliminated.%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20during%20this%20part%20of%20the%20discussion%20that%20he%20accepted%20that%20we%20have%20narratives%20but%20not%20proof%20of%20Balakot%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20there%20is%20a%20substantial%20discussion%20about%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20Balakot%2C%20the%20shooting%20down%20of%20Wing%20Commander%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwhy-iafs-mig-21-grounding-points-to-a-serious-impediment-to-indias-defence-ambitions%5C%22%3EAbhinandan%20Varathaman%E2%80%99s%20MiG-21%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20why%20Pakistan%20chose%20to%20hand%20him%20back%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20part%20of%20the%20interview%20involves%20a%20key%20question%20about%20Biswaria%E2%80%99s%20view%20that%20Pakistan%20%E2%80%9Cpanicked%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20