ic%20by%20suggesting%20a%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Bar%20and%20Bench%2C%20the%20suit%20contends%20that%20Daryaganj%20is%20falsely%20creating%20an%20association%20with%20Moti%20Mahal%2C%20whose%20first%20branch%20was%20established%20in%20Daryaganj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sanjeev%20Narula%2C%20hearing%20the%20case%2C%20has%20asked%20the%20owners%20of%20Daryaganj%20restaurant%20to%20file%20a%20written%20response%20within%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20restaurant%20chains%20have%2C%20for%20years%2C%20claimed%20that%20they%20invented%20Butter%20Chicken%20and%20Dal%20Makhani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoti%20Mahal%20attributes%20the%20creation%20to%20their%20founder%20Kundal%20Lal%20Gujral%2C%20and%20argues%20that%20these%20dishes%20have%20become%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20cuisine%20globally%20due%20to%20Mr%20Gujral's%20culinary%20genius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20claims%20that%20Mr%20Gujral%20was%20concerned%20about%20his%20unsold%20tandoori%20chicken%20drying%20out.%20He%20came%20up%20with%20a%20sauce%20to%20rehydrate%20the%20chicken%2C%20thus%20giving%20birth%20to%20Butter%20Chicken%2C%20Moti%20Mahal%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Daryaganj%20claims%20that%20Kundal%20Lal%20Jaggi%20came%20up%20with%20the%20dishes%2C%20refuting%20the%20lawsuit%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20representing%20Daryaganj%20argued%20that%20the%20original%20Moti%20Mahal%20restaurant%20was%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20predecessors%20of%20both%20parties%20-%20Gujral%20of%20Moti%20Mahal%20and%20Jaggi%20of%20Daryaganj%20-%20in%20Peshawar%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20reports%20Bar%20and%20Bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20next%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20May%2029%2C%20until%20then%20the%20sizzling%20debate%20over%20who%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Binventor%20of%20butter%20chicken%20and%20dal%20makhani%26quot%3B%20will%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705747020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9gc1r9u_butter-chicken_625x300_20_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-invented-butter-chicken-2-delhi-restaurants-battle-it-out-in-court-4898475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20battle%20for%20the%20culinary%20crown%20over%20the%20invention%20of%20iconic%20Indian%20dishes%2C%20Butter%20Chicken%20and%20Dal%20Makhani%2C%20has%20landed%20in%20the%20halls%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-invented-butter-chicken-2-delhi-restaurants-battle-it-out-in-court-4898475%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-invented-butter-chicken-2-delhi-restaurants-battle-it-out-in-court-4898475%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-invented-butter-chicken-2-delhi-restaurants-battle-it-out-in-court-4898475%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2213%20students%20dead%20in%20China%20school%20fire%3A%20Reports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705746962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107012182%2Cimgsize-776709.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftragedy-in-china-13-students-killed-in-school-fire%2Farticleshow%2F107011739.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107011739.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThirteen%20school%20children%20died%20in%20a%20dormitory%20fire%20at%20the%20Yingcai%20School%20in%20Henan%20province%2C%20China.%20The%20fire%20was%20reported%20to%20the%20local%20fire%20department%20and%20extinguished.%20One%20student%20was%20injured%20and%20is%20receiving%20treatment.%20