o-heimplatz-fVL0zZdk-R4-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20has%20issued%20guidelines%20to%20those%20facilitating%20religious%20conversions%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20during%20the%20process%20the%20facilitators%20must%20provide%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20religion%20that%20a%20person%20is%20converting%20to%2C%20its%20associated%20ramifications%2C%20and%20make%20the%20person%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20shifts%20in%20legal%20standing%2C%20post-conversion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Finterfaith-marriage-delhi-hc-decrees-guidelines-for-changing-religion-101705687227561.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConversion%20to%20another%20religion%20which%20is%20uninformed%20may%20not%20prepare%20a%20convert%20with%20the%20consequences%20that%20they%20will%20now%20not%20be%20able%20to%20follow%20their%20form%20of%20religion%20in%20case%20the%20religion%20they%20are%20converting%20to%2C%20does%20not%20permit%20so.%20This%20becomes%20more%20critical%20in%20case%20their%20reverting%20back%20to%20their%20religion%20may%20ensue%20legal%2C%20matrimonial%2C%20succession%2C%20and%20custody-related%20consequences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20the%20guidelines%20as%20part%20of%20a%20case%20it%20was%20hearing%20on%20Friday%2C%20January%2019%2C%20where%20a%20Muslim%20man%20petitioned%20the%20court%20to%20quash%20a%20rape%20complaint%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20a%20Hindu%20woman%20in%20October%202022.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20November%2018%2C%202022%20and%20was%20granted%20interim%20bail%20five%20days%20later%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20they%20had%20married%20according%20to%20Muslim%20customs%20and%20rights%20after%20the%20woman%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20He%20was%20granted%20regular%20in%20February%202023%20after%20the%20woman%20told%20the%20authorities%20that%20she%20married%20the%20man%2010%20days%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20then%20approached%20the%20court%20for%20the%20FIR%20against%20him%20to%20be%20quashed%20and%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20had%20settled%20his%20disputes%20with%20the%20woman%20and%20they%20were%20now%20legally%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20declined%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR.%20Instead%2C%20the%20court%2C%20in%20a%2053-page%20verdict%2C%20issued%20guidelines%20to%20authorities%2Findividuals%20facilitating%20conversion%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20inform%20the%20individual%20with%20exhaustive%20information%20concerning%20the%20religious%20doctrines%2C%20customs%2C%20and%20practices%20associated%20with%20the%20chosen%20faith%20in%20a%20native%20language%20to%20ensure%20that%20consent%20to%20such%20conversion%20is%20an%20informed%20consent%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEqually%20important%20is%20the%20exploration%20of%20religious%20repercussions.%20The%20individual%20must%20be%20apprised%20of%20the%20religious%20norms%2C%20obligations%2C%20and%20restrictions%20that%20come%20with%20the%20conversion%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20told%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20obtain%20an%20affidavit%20from%20the%20parties%20wishing%20to%20convert%20indicating%20their%20age%2C%20marital%20history%2C%20and%20marital%20status%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20interfaith%20marriage.%20It%20also%20said%20affidavits%20must%20be%20obtained%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20conversion%20is%20voluntary%20after%20understanding%20the%20implications%20related%20to%20marital%20divorce%2C%20succession%2C%20custody%2C%20and%20religious%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20Justice%20Sharma%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20illiterate%20and%20did%20not%20know%20Urdu%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENikahnama%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20showed%20that%20the%20contents%20of%20either%20the%20marriage%20or%20conversion%20certificate%20which%20were%20also%20in%20Urdu%20were%20explained%20to%20her.%20She%20refused%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705737948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F21092005%2Fpablo-heimplatz-fVL0zZdk-R4-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-issues-guidelines-for-couples-converting-religion-for-the-sake-of-marriages%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20the%20facilitators%20must%20provide%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20religion%20that%20a%20person%20is%20converting%20to%2C%20its%20associated%20ramifications%2C%20and%20make%20the%20person%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20shifts%20in%20legal%20standing%2C%20post-conversion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-issues-guidelines-for-couples-converting-religion-for-the-sake-of-marriages%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%2014%20Months%20Of%20Training%20For%20Ishq%20Jaisa...%2C%20Hrithik%20Earned%20His%20Reward%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ffighter-song-ishq-jaisa-kuch-we-dare-you-to-look-away-from-deepika-padukone-hrithik-roshan-4722081%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1705820381667000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3jddqVTqxO5wEoQJqrueiY%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ffighter-song-ishq-jaisa-kuch-we-dare-you-to-look-away-from-deepika-padukone-hrithik-roshan