n%20and%20children%20are%20the%20first%20victims%20of%20conflict%20and%20that%20our%20duty%20to%20seek%20peace%20is%20a%20duty%20to%20them.%20We%20are%20failing%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUN%20Women%3C%2Fa%3E%20Executive%20Director%20Sima%20Bahous%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fen%2Fnews-stories%2Fstatement%2F2024%2F01%2Fstatement-on-gaza-by-un-women-executive-director-sima-bahous%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20alongside%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20failure%2C%20and%20the%20generational%20trauma%20inflicted%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20over%20these%20100%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20will%20haunt%20all%20of%20us%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20of%207th%20October%20and%20the%20horrors%20that%20have%20followed%2C%20especially%20in%20Gaza%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20evidenced%20once%20more%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20the%20first%20victims%20of%20conflict.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatement%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Funwomenchief%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40unwomenchief%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sima%20Bahous%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRWf2vhOI7E%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRWf2vhOI7E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5a9jgKFvyK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5a9jgKFvyK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20Women%20(%40UN_Women)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_Women%2Fstatus%2F1748360205698515306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3