t%20%E2%80%93%2083%25%20%E2%80%93%20were%20at%20least%20partially%20operating%2C%20focused%20mainly%20on%20the%20emergency%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20funding%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fflash-appeal-2023-glance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20Flash%20Appeal%20for%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20directly%20gone%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20the%20course%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20part%20of%20UN%20Women%E2%80%99s%20six-month%20response%20plan%20for%20Gaza%2C%20which%20includes%20providing%20emergency%20food%20assistance%20to%20over%2014%2C000%20female-headed%20households%20and%20supporting%20the%20distribution%20of%20items%20requested%20by%20women%20on%20the%20ground%20such%20as%20clothing%2C%20sanitary%20products%20and%20baby%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20is%20also%20partnering%20with%20women-led%20organizations%20to%20deliver%20gender%20responsive%20services%20for%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20establishing%20women-led%20protection%20and%20response%20committees%20in%20shelters%20and%20convening%20regular%20consultations%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20organizations%20to%20discuss%20the%20challenges%20they%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F01%2F1145707%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705736107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06132249%2FCooking-in-war.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-mothers-killed-each-hour-in-gaza-conflict-un-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20and%20children%20account%20for%20roughly%2070%25%20of%20pe