2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20date%20of%20the%20ruling%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%20the%20order%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepka%20said%20that%20the%20process%20would%20move%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20if%20there%20is%20an%20appeal.%20Even%20if%20there%20is%20no%20appeal%20now%20or%20if%20there%20are%20further%20proceedings%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20extradition%20will%20be%20made%20by%20the%20justice%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20case%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Justice.%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20Pavel%20Blazek%20will%20decide%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20allow%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20extradition%20to%20the%20US%20at%20a%20later%20date%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepka%20said%20minister%20Blazek%20had%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%20to%20ask%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20review%20its%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cif%20the%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20has%20doubts%20about%20the%20correctness%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%20a%20given%20matter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible%20to%20predict%20when%20the%20minister%20will%20make%20a%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20requested%20party%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20use%20all%20available%20means%20to%20prevent%20extradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Repka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%2C%20who%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Delhi%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20June%2030%2C%202023%20at%20the%20Czech%20Republic%E2%80%99s%20Vaclav%20Havel%20airport%20upon%20arriving%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20India%20and%20after%20an%20initial%20request%20from%20the%20US%20based%20on%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20issued%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20sent%20a%20formal%20request%20for%20extradition%20to%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20in%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20sealed%20indictment%20against%20Gupta%20had%20been%20filed%20earlier%20at%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20name%20only%20became%20public%20after%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20released%20the%20new%20detailed%20charges%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20charges%20also%20said%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Gupta%20had%2C%20allegedly%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%2C%20hired%20a%20hitman%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20actually%20an%20undercover%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20to%20kill%20a%20lawyer%20working%20for%20a%20Khalistani%20group%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20name%20of%20the%20target%20was%20not%20released%20by%20US%20authorities%2C%20he%20is%20known%20to%20be%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20general%20counsel%20for%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20Khalistani%20group%20banned%20by%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-plot-challenges-extradition-order-czech-court%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20first%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20first%20ruling%20to%20allow%20the%20Czech%20government%20to%20extradite%20Gupta%20was%20made%20by%20a%20lower%20court%20in%20Prague%20on%20November%2023.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20appealed%20this%20ruling%20in%20the%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20businessman%20had%20repeatedly%20asserted%20that%20his%20arrest%20was%20based%20on%20a%20case%20of%20mistaken%20identity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20family%20members%20had%20approached%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20month%2C%20but%20the%20apex%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpannun-murder-plot-sc-junks-plea-against-nikhil-guptas-arrest-cites-lack-of-jurisdiction%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erefused%20to%20intervene%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20ruling%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20January.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705691701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20004338%2FPrague-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fczech-high-court-allows-nikhil-gupta-extradition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20appeals%20the%20High%20Court's%20decision%2C%20the%20matter%20will%20go%20to%20the%20country's%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20first%20ruling%20allowing%20the%20Czech%20government%20to%20extradite%20him%20was%20made%20by%20a%20lower%20court%20in%20Prague%20in%20November.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fczech-high-court-allows-nikhil-gupta-extradition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Th%C3%A9o%20Luhaka%3A%20French%20police%20officers%20given%20suspended%20sentences%20for%20brutal%20assault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705691464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F11EF1%2Fproduction%2F_132375437_gettyimages-1910846066.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68034899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Th%C3%A9o%20Luhaka%20suffered%20severe%20injuries%20from%20a%20police%20baton%20in%20a%20case%20which%20triggered%20days%20of%20protests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A82%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68034899%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68034899.amp%22%2C%22a