%20semester%20mocking%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20after%20dropping%20out%20of%20college%2C%20Shanker%20tried%20his%20hands%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282454%2Fmother-son-duo-leenas-how-to-grow-mushroom-farm-earnings-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20product%20was%20new%20at%20that%20time%20and%20was%20popular%20in%20hotels.%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20business%20would%20boom%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202015%2C%20Shanker%20went%20to%20the%20ICAR-Directorate%20of%20Mushroom%20Research%20in%20Solan%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20cultivating%20mushrooms.%20Coming%20back%2C%20he%20vacated%20a%20small%20room%20of%20his%20house%20and%20set%20up%20the%20base%20for%20cultivating%20mushrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-2-1705068100.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shanker%20exports%20his%20produce%20to%20neighbouring%20countries%20including%20Bhutan%20and%20Nepal%2C%20and%20the%20UAE.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-2-1705068100.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-2-1705068100-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-2-1705068100-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-2-1705068100-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-2-1705068100-150x7