ained%20popularity%20among%20small-scale%20farmers%20for%20its%20low%20input%20costs%2C%20relatively%20high%20yield%2C%20and%20return%20on%20investment.%20But%2C%20Shanker%20opines%2C%20not%20many%20people%20are%20able%20to%20extract%20as%20much%20profit%20owing%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20scientific%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20we%20became%20successful%20is%20because%20I%20always%20stressed%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20spawns%20that%20is%20usually%20compromised%20in%20this%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explains%20in%20detail%2C%20%E2%80%9CLike%20other%20crops%20of%20wheat%20and%20vegetables%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20a%20seed%20for%20mushrooms.%20It%20is%20a%20fungus%20which%20is%20manufactured%20in%20hygienic%20conditions%20in%20a%20lab.%20We%20require%20a%20tissue%20culture%20and%20mother%20spawn%20to%20multiply%20this%20fungus%20and%20get%20more%20spawns%20for%20commercialisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shanker%20officially%20launched%20his%20company%20which%20he%20runs%20along%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Kanchan%20Meena.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-1705068160-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22